Privacy Policy
12.02.2025
Welcome to
Chat AI
. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our application. By using Chat AI, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
1. Data Collection and Processing
Chat AI does
not collect, store, or process any personal data
from its users. All data you provide during your interaction with the app is processed in real-time by the
ChatGPT server
solely to generate responses.
2. Data Storage
We want to be clear:
We do not store any user data.
Your information is processed temporarily only to deliver responses and is not saved on our servers.
3. Data Usage
Chat AI does
not use your data
for any purpose other than providing you with real-time responses.
No data is used for marketing, analytics, or profiling.
We do not analyze, review, or access your data beyond the immediate processing required to generate responses.
4. Data Sharing with Third Parties
We
do not share, sell, or transfer
any user data to third parties. Since we do not store your data, there is nothing to share.
5. Security
Although Chat AI does not store data, we rely on
ChatGPT servers
, which implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information during processing.
6. Third-Party Services
No
